data.description: This corner lot full brick open floor plan offers plenty of space and possibility. The living room and sit-in kitchen are perfect for guests and entertaining with crown molding for an eloquent touch.  The large primary bedroom has ample natural light and high ceilings. A separate walk in closet, double vanity, and separate tub and shower in the primary bathroom. An additonal full bathroom with double vanity for guests or family ensures privacy. The crown molding adds an elegant touch throughout the interior. This beautifully well maintained home located in Chadwick Pointe is a MUST-SEE!
